    USB peripherals).
    </para>

    <para>
      There is some nice material on
      <link linkend="ioredirref">I/O redirection</link>
      in
      <link xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="http://sunsite.ualberta.ca/Documentation/Gnu/textutils-2.0/html_chapter/textutils_10.html">
